HEADWORD: cloud-cuckoo-land
<hw>cloud-cuckoo-land</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an imaginary place where
fantasy and illusion predominate; it is a place where you say people are
when they seem optimistically out of touch with reality.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cloudily</ent>⟦br⟧
